title: SBI SO Recruitment Notification 2016-17
text: SBI SO Recruitment Notification 2016-17 Dear Readers, SBI has released the notification earlier for recruitment of Specialist Cadre Officer. This recruitment process is for experienced professionals. The online Registration has started from 29th Dec. 2016 and you can register till 13th Jan'17.
